Epidemiological comments: vaccination of the national herd in all the wilayahs [provinces] except in the wilayahs in the south.

Measures applied: stamping out [see comment below]; movement control inside the country; screening; vaccination in response to the outbreak(s); disinfection of infected premises/establishment(s); no treatment of affected animals

